108
00:07:07,044 --> 00:07:08,261
Good-bye.

109
00:07:08,296 --> 00:07:09,512
Oh, charlie.

110
00:07:09,547 --> 00:07:11,380
Will you give
susan my best?

111
00:07:11,415 --> 00:07:13,266
And tell her when
you get settled,

112
00:07:13,301 --> 00:07:14,517
to please come over.

113
00:07:14,552 --> 00:07:15,768
Though i expect

114
