if it were jud
come home to me,

117
00:07:23,276 --> 00:07:25,144
i'd hold him
close, so close,

118
00:07:25,179 --> 00:07:27,029
i'd not let him
leave again.

119
00:07:27,064 --> 00:07:28,281
I'm sure, lavinia.

120
