behind, my dear?

388
00:22:39,858 --> 00:22:44,863
Maybe... maybe
it's not so wise.

389
00:22:46,732 --> 00:22:48,617
I'm afraid.

390
00:22:48,652 --> 00:22:51,119
Of course you are.

391
00:22:51,737 --> 00:22:53,622
And i am, too.

392
00:22:55,741 --> 00:23:01,630
"Of all the wonders
that i yet have heard

393
00:23:01,665 --> 00:23:04,132
"it seems to me
most strange

394
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,635
